data.description: Gorgeous one bedroom apartment in the heart of Hallandale Beach.   1 Bedroom 1 bath, Apartment which, offers an inviting eat-in kitchen with stainless steel refrigerator, double sinks, garbage disposal. New floor in the living room, bathroom with  sliding glass doors, accordion shutters. Low maintenance. Perfect move in conditions. A storage locker is included outside the unit. Cable included in the maintenance. Amenities included, clubhouse with sauna, heated pool. NO LEASES, NO PETS. AS IS  Just 1 mile from the beach, close to shops.  grocery stores, Starbucks, Winn Dixie/Publix, coffee shops, restaurants, and the Gulf Stream, Casino, Aventura Mall
